{
 "name": "RPlog_Prophecy",
 "title": "Prophecy",
 "summary": "On the serene bridge of the elegant ship Refrain of Anshalar, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios experiences a profound Force vision touching on the spectres of Chandrila, her master Aurejin, and the pilot Kyyel Marrak. The vision plays out themes of despair, survival, and unyielding hope, affirming Jessalyn as the 'Jedi's Heart' who will not merely survive but thrive against the dangers lurking ahead. Radiating hopeful energy, she emerges from the experience renewed, laughing lightly before retiring to her quarters. The log unfolds as a luminous meditation on prophecy and the resilience of hope.",
